Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:12.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU] Okay, okay,\Nlet's all calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:16.27,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away this\Ntime, you naughty laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:17.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Hmm...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.86,0:00:24.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:26.69,Main,,0,0,0,,It's awfully beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:01:59.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Her scrunchie...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:05.33,Main,,0,0,0,,She still has it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.46,0:02:08.96,Main,,0,0,0,,You remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.04,0:02:10.75,Main,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:13.05,Main,,0,0,0,,...I've known for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:17.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Ever since... our last battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:18.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:19.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:20.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:22.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:23.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Mama is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.77,0:02:25.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Hang on, Hitoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:27.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] It hurt so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.98,0:02:32.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Like my heart was being torn\Ninto a thousand pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.53,0:02:34.53,Main,,0,0,0,,But even through\Nall that pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:36.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I kept thinking:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:38.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't... forget them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:39.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE'S MOTHER gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:40.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE'S MOTHER] Hitoe...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.78,0:02:42.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] But I knew what\Nit meant to lose you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:45.37,Main,,0,0,0,,and I knew that pain\Nwould be even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.46,0:02:47.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:48.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.84,0:02:51.67,Main,,0,0,0,,But wait, if you remembered,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:53.34,Main,,0,0,0,,then why didn't you\Ntell us sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:55.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] Because I wanted\Nmy wish to come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:57.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Because I wanted to win...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:01.64,Main,,0,0,0,,The wish itself\Ndidn't matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:04.73,Main,,0,0,0,,If I won enough, Yuzuki\Nwould complete the oath again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:06.81,Main,,0,0,0,,like she did with Hanayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:10.11,Main,,0,0,0,,And then she'd be\Nfreed from the card!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:11.94,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:16.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] What're you\Nsaying, Hitoe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.49,0:03:18.95,Main,,0,0,0,,That wouldn't solve anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:21.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You'd end up like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:24.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm flattered you care\Nso much, but please,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:26.25,Main,,0,0,0,,don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.33,0:03:28.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't see this\Nas a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:30.79,Main,,0,0,0,,In fact, it's more like\Na dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:34.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Being with friends, making a\Nnoble sacrifice to save them...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:37.13,Main,,0,0,0,,It's all just\Nso romantic...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:41.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm happy such a\Nbeautiful thing even exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:44.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course, the battles\Nand stuff are incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.85,0:03:46.69,Main,,0,0,0,,But meeting\Nthe two of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:49.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Seeing what real\Nfriendship is like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:50.85,Main,,0,0,0,,To me, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:52.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:54.44,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like a miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] Finding a friend who can\Ndo something important for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:06.87,Main,,0,0,0,,and being able to give\Nsomething back to that friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:08.29,Main,,0,0,0,,If I have that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:11.79,Main,,0,0,0,,then there's not a single\Nwish in the world I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:12.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Hitoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.79,0:04:18.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:21.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Doing something\Nfor a friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:22.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Please, Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:24.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:26.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Will you finally\Nlisten to my wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:28.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:30.56,Main,,0,0,0,,We have to free\NYuzuki from the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:33.36,Main,,0,0,0,,There's a chance\Nto save my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:35.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing's more\Nimportant than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:36.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:41.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:46.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want you\Nto be so sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:48.50,Main,,0,0,0,,If I help, will you be\Nfriends with me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:50.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:53.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:55.38,Main,,0,0,0,,You tell Tama what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:56.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:59.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Battling's about\Nall I'm good for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:02.80,Main,,0,0,0,,But if that can make\Nyour wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:07.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll battle and battle\Nas much as it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.14,0:05:09.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:11.89,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:13.40,Main,,0,0,0,,You ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:15.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's continue the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:16.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, but Hitoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:17.94,Main,,0,0,0,,One last thing:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:19.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.15,0:05:21.03,Main,,0,0,0,,But there's no way I'll lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:22.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I've made my wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:24.16,Main,,0,0,0,,and it's coming true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:25.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Attack: Arc Aura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:35.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:43.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Good game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:44.80,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:50.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] I lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.14,0:05:54.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Hope that\Ndidn't hurt, Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:55.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Only my pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:56.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:58.23,Main,,0,0,0,,What about your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:05:59.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:01.07,Main,,0,0,0,,You finally figured it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:04.28,Main,,0,0,0,,It's clear now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.36,0:06:07.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I want Yuzuki and all the\Nother girls trapped in cards
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:09.04,Main,,0,0,0,,to be free...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:09.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko, that's--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:11.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Whoa-whoa-whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:12.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:14.46,Main,,0,0,0,,We need to talk about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:15.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] But we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:18.84,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the ones who made me\Nrealize what I needed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.92,0:06:23.09,Main,,0,0,0,,If there's something I can do\Nfor my friends, I should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:26.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing would make me\Nhappier and that's final.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:32.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd better be going...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:35.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:37.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm coming with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:39.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Meaning we're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.11,0:06:42.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Then-- you're\Nokay with my wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:42.86,Main,,0,0,0,,You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:45.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:47.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Not like I could\Nchange your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:50.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Just make sure you get\Nyour wish right, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:52.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, yeah, duh, I want\Nto get out of this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:54.12,Main,,0,0,0,,But this'll be all for nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.17,Main,,0,0,0,,if you end up as\Na LRIG yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:58.88,Main,,0,0,0,,We're getting dumplings on the\Nway home and I want you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:16.52,Main,,0,0,0,,So, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:18.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to go\Nshopping with you, Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:20.31,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:21.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Can we eat dumplings?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:23.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I was thinking I'd buy\Nyou some scrunchies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:26.15,Main,,0,0,0,,So you can match the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:27.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:41.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:45.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] Oh, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:47.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Not good with heights...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:51.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd feel better about it if\NI could pick out my apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:52.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:59.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:00.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:05.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] I've been expecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:06.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Hi, Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:08.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.32,0:08:09.78,Main,,0,0,0,,And you brought\Nyour little friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:10.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:12.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah? What's it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:14.08,Main,,0,0,0,,She is our friend, and we're\Nhere to support her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:16.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] Fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:18.46,Main,,0,0,0,,A cheering section won't\Nmake any difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:19.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:21.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Anything else, Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:23.67,Main,,0,0,0,,A rousing speech, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:25.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Or something you'd\Nlike to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:32.14,Main,,0,0,0,,No questions. No speeches.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:34.47,Main,,0,0,0,,All I want is to battle you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:36.35,Main,,0,0,0,,You really are the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:41.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA & RUKO] Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:56.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] What a dark\Nand lonely place...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:59.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it always so\Nscary when you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:01.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:03.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought you were\Nall out of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:06.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Ready when you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You're up first, Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:26.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:29.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA shouts]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:30.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:32.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:36.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:38.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:40.29,Main,,0,0,0,,They're both so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:41.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] But look at Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:45.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Something's off...\NHer eyes are so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:49.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I don't get this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:54.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Battles before were always fun,\Nor exciting, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:56.64,Main,,0,0,0,,This is just... hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:03.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] It's so quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:07.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA breathing]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.77,0:10:10.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I can even\Nhear Tama breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:14.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] This may\Nbe my final battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:17.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't have any doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:18.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, Grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:22.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Use: Sword Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:30.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Haah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:31.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:36.05,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH pants]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:37.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Focus...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:39.26,Main,,0,0,0,,She's one of a kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:40.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Gotta give her that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:44.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] Of course, you have\Nmore than enough wins
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:45.52,Main,,0,0,0,,to have your wish granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:48.27,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just the time\Nwasn't quite ripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:50.86,Main,,0,0,0,,This might give it the\N"push" you need, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:53.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Assuming you're ready, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:55.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Not just yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:57.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, Grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:11:00.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Trust me, it won't\Nbe much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:03.96,Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't for my sake,\Nbut for Ru's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:06.50,Main,,0,0,0,,My Dear Ruko Kominato!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:08.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Black Desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:11.75,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:13.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:19.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:20.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:26.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:27.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:29.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:37.03,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:38.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:39.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] That's not Ru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:40.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:44.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] But I know that voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:46.08,Main,,0,0,0,,...better than Ru's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:48.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe better than my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:52.21,Main,,0,0,0,,It must've been from\Na long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:54.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] You've finally\Ncome to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.47,0:11:56.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:58.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:12.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] You poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:16.15,Main,,0,0,0,,All the pain she's\Nput you through.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:17.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:19.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] Ru is... so cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:22.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:25.41,Main,,0,0,0,,A wish to be together...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:28.50,Main,,0,0,0,,To never draw apart,\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:31.63,Main,,0,0,0,,A dream that you believed in\Nwith all your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:35.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] I know you love Ru,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:37.88,Main,,0,0,0,,but she cares for her\Nfriends more than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:38.72,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:40.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:42.05,Main,,0,0,0,,You got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:43.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:45.14,Main,,0,0,0,,She said she'd be\Nfriends with me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:46.64,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:49.48,Main,,0,0,0,,After this, we were gonna go\Neat ice cream and dumplings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:51.56,Main,,0,0,0,,And then I was gonna\Nget a matching scrunchie
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:53.40,Main,,0,0,0,,so I could be like\Nher other friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:55.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:57.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:13:00.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] It's true that\NRu loves her friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:03.62,Main,,0,0,0,,She loves them so much\Nthat she lied to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:05.95,Main,,0,0,0,,And now she's going to\Nbecome an LRIG for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:07.37,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] That's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:09.96,Main,,0,0,0,,We're all going home\Ntogether after this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:11.08,Main,,0,0,0,,So I have to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:13.08,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] That won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:14.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Please listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:17.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, try to remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:28.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRLS crying & moaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:29.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] The solution is easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:32.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:35.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] You want to stop Ru from\Nbecoming an LRIG, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:37.73,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't have\Nto lose the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:39.78,Main,,0,0,0,,You can refuse the\Nwish at the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:41.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:43.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] Yuzuki said the\Nsame thing, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:45.91,Main,,0,0,0,,For a Selector's wish\Nto be fulfilled,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:48.37,Main,,0,0,0,,the LRIG must be in agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:52.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] But then, what will\Nhappen to Ru's wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:54.50,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] Win the battle and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:55.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:58.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Then you'll know\Nher true feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:14:01.17,Main,,0,0,0,,and you'll see why I'm\Ntrying to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:02.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Protect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.01,0:14:04.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] But only if you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:07.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:09.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:11.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you able\Nto get back up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:15.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] I'll find out\Nher true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:18.23,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're still hurt,\Ndon't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:21.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] I'll fight and\NI'll win the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:24.41,Main,,0,0,0,,And then, it\Nwill all be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:25.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:28.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] That's a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:31.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Hate to see you give up\Nwhen it's just getting fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:32.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:33.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Drawing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:34.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Ener Charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:36.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama to Level 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:40.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] No matter what\Nhappens after my wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:41.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] ...this is\Nthe last battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.05,0:14:43.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I don't know\Nif it'll come true,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:45.22,Main,,0,0,0,,or if everything\Nwill fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:47.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] But we have to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:48.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO & TAMA] This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.27,0:14:53.64,Main,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:54.81,Main,,0,0,0,,It's not an attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.89,0:14:56.31,Main,,0,0,0,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.90,0:14:59.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] The battlefield's\Ncoming apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:18.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] The roof...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:21.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Were we kicked out of the\Nbattlefield for some reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:24.67,Main,,0,0,0,,No, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:26.13,Main,,0,0,0,,The sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:28.22,Main,,0,0,0,,And it seems like\Nthey're still fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:35.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH giggles]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:39.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, Ru, what should\NI do for my next attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:44.61,Main,,0,0,0,,It's so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:51.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] And I just noticed... you\Ncan see our apartment from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:54.16,Main,,0,0,0,, That does make me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:55.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.08,0:15:56.12,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:57.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Thanks, Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:58.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] You wanted me\Nto see it one last time
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:02.80,Main,,0,0,0,,before the end, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:05.17,Main,,0,0,0,,The end?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:06.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Bye, Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.59,0:16:11.72,Main,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:12.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:14.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:15.93,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] Can you\Nbelieve it, Iona?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:18.23,Main,,0,0,0,,She thinks she's\Nalready won this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:20.90,Main,,0,0,0,,She's the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:23.90,Main,,0,0,0,,She honestly is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:25.74,Main,,0,0,0,,My Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:27.36,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] What's the\Nnext step, Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:28.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:34.12,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Before the\Nlast attack, an oath...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:37.29,Main,,0,0,0,,'Kay, I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:41.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] That's right,\Nbefore my wish was granted,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:43.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I took an oath with Hanayo, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.71,0:16:46.88,Main,,0,0,0,,It seals the final contract\Nbetween you and your LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:50.97,Main,,0,0,0,,But wait, if Tama lost her\Nmemory, how does she know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:02.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell me what to say\Nand I'll say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.03,0:17:08.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Maybe...\Nshe was lying to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:11.53,Main,,0,0,0,,She's not thinking\Nabout going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.61,0:17:13.49,Main,,0,0,0,,She never was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:18.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] She thinks the only way\Nshe can save her friends
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:20.50,Main,,0,0,0,,is to become an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:21.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] She knew I\Nwouldn't agree with this
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:24.42,Main,,0,0,0,,if she told me the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:26.67,Main,,0,0,0,,She wants to\Nsacrifice herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:29.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:32.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Please. Just tell\Nme what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:36.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I accept the laws,\Nthe laws of--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:38.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I accept the laws of?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:41.31,Main,,0,0,0,,The laws of the... Selector...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:43.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] I accept the\Nlaws of the Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:45.40,Main,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:48.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:50.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:58.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:01.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:03.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] Ugh! This\Nis taking forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:05.63,Main,,0,0,0,,The battle's almost over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:07.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Can't we do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:09.34,Main,,0,0,0,,It's our turn, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:11.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's just finish 'em off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:15.14,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] Urith, Bloody Slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:18.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:20.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH] Use White Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.90,0:18:26.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:31.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[crashing]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:33.32,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRLS screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.40,0:18:34.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[SELECTOR D] Uh-oh.\NWhat's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.99,0:18:36.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Hang on,\Nis this normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:40.66,Main,,0,0,0,,[MIDORIKO] It's happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:42.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.34,0:18:54.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki, what're\Nyou looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:57.85,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:19:00.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO (Y) sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:02.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.02,0:19:06.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Don't worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:09.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't have a single regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:11.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Because no matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.44,0:19:14.90,Main,,0,0,0,,this was the wish that\NI chose for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:16.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm happy to make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:18.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:30.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:32.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:34.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko won, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:36.76,Main,,0,0,0,,But the contract\Nwasn't completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:37.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:39.85,Main,,0,0,0,,They skipped\Nthe last part.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.93,0:19:41.77,Main,,0,0,0,,It goes: "And upon\Nthis sacred oath,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:44.27,Main,,0,0,0,,a new Eternal Girl\Nshall be born!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:46.89,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:48.69,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] I can't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:51.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if you earned your wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:54.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't let you\Nturn into an LRIG!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:57.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:19:58.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:01.91,Main,,0,0,0,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:06.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:08.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, it's going away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:11.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Finish the oath! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:14.42,Main,,0,0,0,,No! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:24.64,Main,,0,0,0,,This is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:30.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] But... I won\Nthe battle, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:32.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] Aww, don't\Nlook so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:35.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona's been ready to have her\Nwish granted for some time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:39.61,Main,,0,0,0,,She's won a whole ton of\NSelector battles, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:42.33,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just we had to wait\Nfor a certain "condition"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.41,0:20:45.74,Main,,0,0,0,,to fall into place before\Nwe could seal the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:46.75,Main,,0,0,0,,"Condition"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:47.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH] That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:50.42,Main,,0,0,0,,But now the condition\Nhas been met.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:53.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Hope you're happy, you've\Nbeen waiting long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:55.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] That I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:57.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Not that I'm complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:00.72,Main,,0,0,0,,But, what about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:03.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:06.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO sobs]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:08.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.31,0:21:10.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Snap out of it! Why\Nwon't you grant my wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:12.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:14.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:18.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA & URITH] I accept...\Nthe laws of the Selector.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:20.49,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] No, You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:24.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Please,\Njust listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:27.79,Main,,0,0,0,,We have to turn everyone\Nback to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:29.20,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA & URITH] "And upon\Nthis sacred oath,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:32.54,Main,,0,0,0,,a new Eternal Girl\Nshall be born!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:34.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:03.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait... Iona, you're...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.70,0:22:05.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I) chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.33,0:22:12.16,Main,,0,0,0,,No, Urith...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.25,0:22:16.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's do this again sometime,\NMiss Pain-in-the-ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.88,0:22:22.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.01,0:22:24.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama, why did--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.72,0:22:28.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:29.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Where did she--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.93,0:22:31.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.02,0:22:36.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] Oh, this\Nis gonna be fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.90,0:22:37.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Hi, Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.77,0:22:39.19,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.11,0:22:46.57,Main,,0,0,0,,[AYUMU] Ah, so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.66,0:22:49.83,Main,,0,0,0,,You really outdid yourself on\Nthe sauce this time, Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.91,0:22:52.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[HATSU chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.54,0:22:55.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru must be having fun\Nand lost track of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.21,0:22:56.21,Main,,0,0,0,,She'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.29,0:22:57.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Just eat already.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.59,0:23:01.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Not yet, I made\Nthis just for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.51,0:23:03.84,Main,,0,0,0,,When we eat, we do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.51,0:23:10.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] You told me... we'd\Ndo everything together, Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.52,0:23:11.89,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.97,0:23:13.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.14,0:23:15.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.39,0:23:17.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Tamaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.86,0:23:23.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Being with\Nyou... is my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.24,0:23:31.83,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)] Ah, we meet again,\NMiss Pain-in-the-ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:33.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] So, Ru, who's\Nour first opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.79,0:23:34.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:36.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Was it because\NI did something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.75,0:23:38.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO\N'Cause you're my friend, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.13,0:23:39.17,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.80,0:23:45.92,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Next:\N"Selector Spread WIXOSS."
